{"tid":814374,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"單文柔多謝陳展鵬 「成為你生命中女主角」","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T01:01:51.000Z","uid":160973,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"235418a1ceb15f412b6f3ca3dd6123edb54ac05e","tid":814374,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:03:57.000Z","msg":"四十一歲陳展鵬公開喜訊，與廿八歲單文柔十月拉埋天窗，在港擺酒，繼昨日求婚篇後，今日就有認定篇，今早準新郎對準時間0909於微博上載與女友拍攝婚紗照的花絮，更留言「是她」，再以一張單人側面低頭照，寫上「May I？」相當有心思。其後又再IG上載照片，其中一張兩人更深情對望，他更寫上「也是唯一的」，甜蜜指數爆燈，難怪準新娘單文柔亦相當冧爆，公開留言回應，「多謝你讓我成為你生命中的女主角！」<br />\n<br />\n單文柔話公開婚訊後，呢刻心情依然好興奮，「今次展鵬安排咗好多，製造咗好多好靚的畫面！影咗好多靚相！所以好感激佢對我的好！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oWoJbh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oWoJbh&d=tYIKVQDHuTuwEEk%2FJ6p%2FTAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5d02d610\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oWoJbh</a>"},{"pid":"5b837d052890d2b1d99f41b5a5122bb5d765f856","tid":814374,"uid":179782,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"恭喜 <br />\n如果煎pan考慮退出幕前就更好"},{"pid":"393a246223cc33c7f1ea1174e6ccd3b1e8a3e1a8","tid":814374,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"要同亞視仔做愛 被佢抽插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"95dae4e02125c7a6f59263fb4078314c5678dfa1","tid":814374,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af651d8f6fba4dd4ef4986c11f6089874267d333","tid":814374,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"兩個邊個有錢啲？"},{"pid":"4e48e9830db4c00ef38ffeeb4a7de53498ed9b90","tid":814374,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"如我未配擔演主角 甘願作丑角"},{"pid":"65bb3a7a87217fdb64b055e437d10ad2aec14694","tid":814374,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T22:39:59.00